#

Classic Ukrainian Borshch

110 min
$12.5
250 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 6

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

Ukrainian

Course:

Main Course

Tags:

SoupComfort FoodTraditionalHearty

Description

A hearty and vibrant beet soup, rich in flavor and tradition, perfect for a comforting meal.

Ingredients

  • beets: 3 large
  • cabbage: 1/2 head
  • potatoes: 2 medium
  • carrots: 2 medium
  • onion: 1 medium
  • garlic: 3 cloves
  • vegetable broth: 6 cups
  • tomato paste: 2 tablespoons
  • fresh dill: 1/4 cup
  • bay leaves: 2
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • vegetable oil: 2 tablespoons
  • sour cream: for serving
